cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite it as below."
title: "Peptide Visual Lab (PVL)"
type: software
version: "0.3.0"
date-released: "2026-06-08"
abstract: >-
  An all-in-one peptide aggregation + structure prediction dashboard.
  Combines aggregation propensity (TANGO), secondary structure prediction
  (S4PRED), fibril-forming helix detection (FF-Helix), secondary structure
  switch (SSW) prediction, and live AlphaFold 3D structure overlay with
  reproducibility-as-permalink and hover-everywhere drill-down. Designed
  as a multi-surface AI-platform-ready research instrument (web + Python
  package + CLI + planned MCP server).
